of the change in

00:12:01.560 --> 00:12:02.730
enthalpy of formation.

00:12:02.730 --> 00:12:04.740
So it's going to be a positive
number there.

00:12:04.740 --> 00:12:08.470
We add to that the enthalpy for
this reaction here, which

00:12:08.470 --> 00:12:10.110
is negative 393 .

00:12:10.110 --> 00:12:13.500
5, but we need to remember to
multiply that by 6, because

00:12:13.500 --> 00:12:15.460
we're actually adding
together six of

00:12:15.460 --> 00:12:17.710
those individual reactions.

