as we could say, some

00:26:30.600 --> 00:26:33.490
of the enthalpy that's released
in terms of forming

00:26:33.490 --> 00:26:35.510
and breaking the bonds
in a reaction.

00:26:35.510 --> 00:26:38.170
So that's our case where we
could see that we have a

00:26:38.170 --> 00:26:40.820
