00:34:25.950 --> 00:34:29.880
this makes me full of joy.
"Something there is that

00:34:29.880 --> 00:34:33.050
doesn't love a wall," there's
many interpretations for this

00:34:33.050 --> 00:34:35.050
poem, but maybe it's
about entropy.

00:34:35.050 --> 00:34:38.980
Entropy doesn't love a wall,
we're going from order to

00:34:38.980 --> 00:34:41.290
disorder, that wall wants
to come down.

00:34:41.290 --> 00:34:44.520
All right.

00:34:44.520 --> 00:34:47.240
So let's formalize these
thoughts on entropy and in

00:34:47.240 --> 00:34:49.460
terms of what we're
talking about.

00:34:49.460 --> 00:34:53.170
Again, what I said on that's
