00:35:26.980 --> 00:35:30.620
So in terms of considering
different types of states that

00:35:30.620 --> 00:35:33.780
we can be in, whether we're in
a gas state or a liquid state

00:35:33.780 --> 00:35:37.020
or a solid state for any given
molecule or any given

00:35:37.020 --> 00:35:41.070
compound, we can think about
how much order or disorder

00:35:41.070 --> 00:35:44.710
these states have. So which of
these three states would you

00:35:44.710 --> 00:35:46.540
call the most disordered?

