00:36:16.660 --> 00:36:20.770
So, just understanding this
explanation of entropy that

00:36:20.770 --> 00:36:24.180
we're going to have an increase
in entropy if we have

00:36:24.180 --> 00:36:27.370
an increase in disorder, allows
